  Create a Restaurant and Dine Out

  Own a restaurant and take your Sims out to eat with The Sims 4 Dine Out.
  Create and manage a variety of restaurants, hire staff, and set the perfect
  menu to earn a profit and expand your business. Dine out with Sims to enjoy
  all-new experimental cuisine and spend quality time with friends and family.
